Class Call

public class Call
extends RPCMessage

A Call object represents an RPC call. Both the client and the server use Call objects to invoke the method.

Author:
Matthew J. Duftler (duftler@us.ibm.com), Sanjiva Weerawarana (sanjiva@watson.ibm.com)
